# Roadmap


## Release 1.0.0 "Stone"

1. Menu bar and keyboard shortcuts
     Possible reason for rejection from the app store
     Breaks the user interface


## Release 1.1.0 "Iron"

1. Ragel parser
     Parse perf. on large templates can blow out to ~5s
     Treetop is an extra dependency
2. Help menubar
3. Better App Store description/screenshots
4. Quick Tumblr Markup icon


## Release 1.2.0 "Coal"

1. Complete data mocking
2. Custom pages
3. Variable transformations


## Release 2.0.0 "Diamond"

1. Parse custom variables
     Pass in runtime options (colors etc.)
2. Parse i18n
3. Design
     Custom widgets/Animations
4. Icon
5. Website
6. Textmate Bundle
7. Remember last template
